address.street1: Capital Mall - 625 Black Lake Boulevard Southwest

notes: This is a single-dose Johnson & Johnson clinic being held at Capital Mall, 625 Black Lake Blvd SW, Olympia WA, 98502 for anyone age 18 and older from 12pm until mall closing. We will be located inside the mall, closest to the Sephora end of the mall and next to the Buckle store. Please bring a form of identification with you to your appointment - ID card, passport, or other document with your name and birthday on it. • Wear a short-sleeved shirt, but dress with layers, if needed. • Waiting at least 15 minutes after vaccination is required.
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

name: Thurston County Public Health Medical Reserve Corp

address.street1: Capital Mall - 625 Black Lake Boulevard Southwest

notes: This is a Pfizer vaccination event for anyone age 12 and older. This is a walk in clinic being held at Capital Mall, 625 Black Lake Blvd SW, Olympia WA, 98502 daily from 12pm until mall closing. We will be located inside the mall, closest to the Sephora end of the mall and next to the Buckle store. • All minors 12 to 17 years old must receive parent or guardian consent to receive a COVID-19 vaccine. This must be done in PrepMod when registering for an appointment. Parents or guardians do not have to be present at the time of vaccination if they signed the consent form online during registration. • Please bring a form of identification with you to your appointment - ID card, passport, or other document with your name and birthday on it. • Wear a short-sleeved shirt, but dress with layers if necessary. • Waiting at least 15 minutes after vaccination is required.
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

name: Yakima County Health District COVID Vaccination Site
notes:
***1ST & 2nd DOSE PFIZER VACCINATIONS!!!!*** The vaccination clinic will take place at Toppenish Flea Market. This clinic will be outside. Masks are required. Please wear clothing which allows access to your shoulder. All individuals 12 and over are eligible to get vaccinated. Those under 18 must be accompanied by a parent/guardian or must get parental consent via video/phone call or paper format.
Informacion Adicional: ***VACUNAS DE PRIMERA Y SEGUNDA DOSIS PFIZER!!!*** La clínica de vacunación se ubicara en la Pulga de Toppenish. Se requieren máscaras. Los menores de 18 años deben estar acompañados por un padre/tutor o deben obtener el consentimiento de los padres por video/llamada telefónica o en papel.
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.
